Spaces increase ➜ i - 1
Stars decrease ➜ 2 * (n - i) + 1

Code
=====

int n = 4;

for (int i = 1; i <= n; i++) {

    // Print spaces
    for (int j = 1; j <= i - 1; j++) {
        System.out.print(" ");
    }

    // Print stars
    for (int j = 1; j <= 2 * (n - i) + 1; j++) {
        System.out.print("*");
    }

    System.out.println();
}
